Hello Usama Aziz,
&nbsp;
Good day!
&nbsp;
Thank you for your interest in the PH Multi Carrier Shipping Label app. It is an advanced Shopify solution that supports 33+ shipping carriers and helps streamline your entire shipping process. This includes displaying real-time calculated rates, generating shipping labels in bulk, sending tracking updates to customers, scheduling pickups, and much more.
&nbsp;
Regarding your queries:
  The app can automatically select the best and most cost-effective available service when generating shipping labels.  You also have the flexibility to manually choose your preferred carrier service from the connected carriers.  The app allows you to generate custom documents such as Commercial Invoice, CN22, and CN23, including details like HS Code, Country of Origin, and product description to ensure smooth customs clearance.  The app supports PostNord integration along with all its available services.  You can connect UPS and other carriers for express shipping options.  Return labels can be generated directly within the app.  The app integrates directly with Shopify to import orders and fulfill them with tracking numbers. However, Amazon MCF cannot be integrated with the app. That said, your Amazon MCF setup will continue to function as it currently does without any interruption.  Additionally, you can schedule pickups within the app, and the respective carrier agent will collect the parcels from your warehouse.  &nbsp;
You can configure shipping rules based on zone, price, quantity, and weight. However, setting rules based on inventory or product availability is not supported at the moment.
&nbsp;
I would be happy to schedule a demo call at your convenience. Before that, could you please let us know the approximate number of orders you expect to process per month?
&nbsp;
Looking forward to your response.

Thanks and Regards,
Manohar V
Team PluginHive

